                <head>320. Editorial Note</head>
                <p>Brazilian President-elect <persName corresp="#p_KOJ1">Kubitschek</persName>
                    arrived in the United States on January 5, 1956, beginning a 6-day unofficial
                    visit. He met first with President <persName corresp="#p_EDD1"
                        >Eisenhower</persName> at Key West, Florida, on the morning of January 5 and
                    traveled to Washington later that day for a series of meetings with United
                    States officials. Documentation on <persName corresp="#p_KOJ1"
                        >Kubitschek</persName>’s visit is in Department of State, Central File
                    033.3211 and <hi rend="italic">ibid.</hi>, <gloss target="#t_ARA1">ARA</gloss>
                    Files: Lot 62 D 308, Visit of President-Elect <persName corresp="#p_KOJ1"
                        >Kubitschek</persName>.</p>
            </div>
